Calculation Groups brings delights to finance professionals by making muticurrency financial reports highly impactful.

In a multicurrency environment making a financial report to show local currency values and making it to switch to a foriegn currency on a click of a button for comparing the results is cumbosrome. 
Thanks to Power BI's calculation groups which enables us (BI Analytsts) for taking up such challenging demands of finance professionals and bring delight to them.
